{"tid":290631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柒柒柒: 香港青年在幼兒階段就該開始培養「我是中國人」","createTime":"2017-06-20T02:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T03:53:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a2941caaaf0ec0b94636ac71089dd7de6d90290","tid":290631,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"候任行政長官林鄭月娥接受新華社專訪。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，希望香港青年能夠被培育成具備香港情懷、國家觀念和世界視野的一代人。她認為，香港情懷和國家觀念完全沒有衝突，既可以讓下一代了解香港的歷史、文化、政治、社會發展情況，同時也必須要讓他們有國民身份的認同。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥認為，在幼兒階段就應該開始培養「我是中國人」的概念，在中小學階段，將中國歷史納入初中必修科目，在學校以外，政府要讓學童接觸更多中國文化，讓香港青年了解國家最新的發展。 <br />\n<br />\n應該學支那高官咁，「我是拿著美國護照的新中國人」"},{"pid":"1f53e3d09b664549d40ec88aab31ad7bcc384701","tid":290631,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"哇屌你老母"},{"pid":"4f4832903eae257f2b2b29b4681c87dfe1144a15","tid":290631,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁撚細個就洗鳩細路腦<br />\n仆街死全家啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死臭閪全家生柳"},{"pid":"d088df87618f7a6aac650b197bb35279167107c8","tid":290631,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母咁撚細個就洗鳩細路腦<br />\n仆街死全家啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死臭閪全家生花柳</blockquote>"},{"pid":"473ffc92e822221ad0ec4d9e80891d60d5e95b71","tid":290631,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:31:24.000Z","msg":"咁細個就唔應該講粗口既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae940a69bae1480a20bd0134c4ee82db42b8610d","tid":290631,"uid":36178,"like":4,"di